1
00:01:06,107 --> 00:01:09,360
INGIN JUMPA TEMAN LELAKI
YANG SETERUSNYA? (YA/TIDAK)

2
00:01:12,363 --> 00:01:14,949
EPISOD 1
MASA DEPAN KAU DAN AKU

3
00:01:33,134 --> 00:01:34,052
DUA MINGGU LALU

4
00:01:34,135 --> 00:01:35,303
Saya dah balik.

5
00:01:37,388 --> 00:01:38,765
Saya dah baliklah.

6
00:01:39,557 --> 00:01:41,267
<i>Mod rumah diaktifkan.</i>

7
00:01:52,362 --> 00:01:53,947
Seronoknya dah balik.

8
00:02:02,789 --> 00:02:04,165
<i>Sehari ada 24 jam.</i>

9
00:02:05,959 --> 00:02:07,293
<i>Tidur enam jam.</i>

10
00:02:07,794 --> 00:02:09,337
<i>Kerja 10 jam.</i>

11
00:02:09,838 --> 00:02:12,006
<i>Pergi balik kerja dan makan…</i>

12
00:02:12,090 --> 00:02:13,383
MAKAN: 1 JAM

13
00:02:13,466 --> 00:02:16,386
<i>Tolak semua itu,</i>
<i>tambah urus diri, tinggallah…</i>

14
00:02:16,469 --> 00:02:17,554
URUS DIRI: 1.5 JAM

15
00:02:17,637 --> 00:02:19,556
<i>…tiga jam setengah.</i>

16
00:02:20,598 --> 00:02:23,434
<i>Cukup untuk tonton</i>
<i>satu atau dua filem saja.</i>

17
00:02:25,687 --> 00:02:30,567
<i>Aku tak bazirkan tiga jam setengah</i>
<i>yang berharga itu untuk sesiapa saja.</i>

18
00:02:39,159 --> 00:02:43,079
<i>Hari biasa seperti hari ini,</i>
<i>tanpa rancangan atau aktiviti khas…</i>

19
00:02:43,788 --> 00:02:44,873
Selesanya.

20
00:02:55,592 --> 00:02:58,011
<i>Hari-hari beginilah yang aku paling suka.</i>

21
00:02:58,511 --> 00:02:59,679
Tidur dulu.

22
00:03:00,221 --> 00:03:02,473
<i>Mod tidur diaktifkan.</i>

23
00:03:15,028 --> 00:03:17,113
<i>Kebahagiaan itu cuma sementara,</i>

24
00:03:17,197 --> 00:03:19,991
<i>sebelum terhumban semula</i>
<i>ke dunia yang sibuk.</i>

25
00:03:25,538 --> 00:03:27,498
ERA CINTA BARU
BOYFRIEND ON DEMAND

26
00:03:27,582 --> 00:03:30,418
<i>Tren laluan bulatan akan tiba…</i>

27
00:04:01,407 --> 00:04:02,825
- Hai.
- Hai.

28
00:04:13,169 --> 00:04:16,464
<i>Musim panas lalu di Filipina</i>
<i>memang seronok betul.</i>

29
00:04:18,091 --> 00:04:19,759
<i>Seronoknya boleh mandi laut.</i>

30
00:04:21,135 --> 00:04:22,679
<i>Bila musim panas nak tiba?</i>

31
00:04:37,944 --> 00:04:38,945
Maaf kacau.

32
00:04:40,989 --> 00:04:42,031
Ya?

33
00:04:42,115 --> 00:04:43,658
Saya rasa budak itu…

34
00:04:51,666 --> 00:04:53,960
<i>Bertuah punya budak!</i>

35
00:05:00,258 --> 00:05:01,592
<i>Pintu dibuka.</i>

36
00:05:07,598 --> 00:05:09,183
<i>Pintu dibuka.</i>

37
00:05:14,731 --> 00:05:16,316
<i>Pintu ditutup.</i>

38
00:05:18,943 --> 00:05:19,777
Helo.

39
00:05:20,945 --> 00:05:21,779
Hai.

40
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:27,285
Kenapa tak bersih?

41
00:05:28,870 --> 00:05:30,455
Macam itu tak bolehlah.

42
00:05:32,874 --> 00:05:33,708
Okey.

43
00:05:36,044 --> 00:05:37,045
<i>Apa masalah dia?</i>

44
00:05:38,629 --> 00:05:40,465
<i>Pintu dibuka.</i>

45
00:05:45,428 --> 00:05:47,180
<i>Pintu ditutup.</i>

46
00:05:53,269 --> 00:05:54,479
TIDAK BERDAFTAR

47
00:05:54,562 --> 00:05:56,439
<i>Sila cuba lagi.</i>

48
00:06:08,284 --> 00:06:09,118
Penerbit!

49
00:06:09,702 --> 00:06:10,536
Helo.

50
00:06:10,620 --> 00:06:11,871
- Baru sampai?
- Hai.

51
00:06:11,954 --> 00:06:13,498
Tahniah.

52
00:06:13,581 --> 00:06:15,375
- Kenapa…
- Tahniah.

53
00:06:20,588 --> 00:06:21,589
Terima kasih.

54
00:06:25,259 --> 00:06:27,762
Macam biasa, sampai tepat pada masanya.

55
00:06:27,845 --> 00:06:30,807
Tak pernah awal seminit pun. Saya tabik.

56
00:06:31,307 --> 00:06:33,142
Ini hari jadi Park Kyeong-nam?

57
00:06:33,226 --> 00:06:37,063
- Tak, dia dapat kontrak adaptasi drama.
- Dapat lagi?

58
00:06:37,146 --> 00:06:40,858
Jomlah, pengarah nak belanja kita
makan daging malam ini.

59
00:06:40,942 --> 00:06:42,068
Keluar makan?

60
00:06:43,611 --> 00:06:45,571
Saya ada hal malam ini.

61
00:06:45,655 --> 00:06:47,865
Ada hal konon.

62
00:06:47,949 --> 00:06:49,951
Cakaplah awak tak makan daging.

63
00:06:50,034 --> 00:06:53,246
Park Kyeong-nam pun pergi, bukan?
Kita nak raikan dia.

64
00:06:53,329 --> 00:06:55,289
Peliklah kalau dia tak pergi.

65
00:06:55,790 --> 00:06:56,999
Betulkah awak tak ikut?

66
00:06:57,500 --> 00:07:02,088
Bos bengang awak jarang-jarang
keluar makan dengan kami.

67
00:07:02,171 --> 00:07:04,173
Bukannya saya saja. Mamat itu…

68
00:07:04,674 --> 00:07:06,634
Park pun jarang pergi.

69
00:07:06,717 --> 00:07:09,554
Betul kata awak.
Dia lebih sombong daripada awak.

70
00:07:09,637 --> 00:07:11,431
Kamu tak rasa dia menawan?

71
00:07:12,432 --> 00:07:13,433
Apa?

72
00:07:15,810 --> 00:07:18,729
Biarkanlah dia. Dia peminat Kyeong-nam.

73
00:07:20,106 --> 00:07:21,357
- Peminat?
- Ya.

74
00:07:21,858 --> 00:07:24,694
Saya dah fikir masak-masak
dan nak cuba suka dia.

75
00:07:26,737 --> 00:07:29,866
Apa? Nak cuba apa? Kenapa?

76
00:07:29,949 --> 00:07:31,409
Sebab dia kacak gila.

77
00:07:33,870 --> 00:07:34,704
Bau pun wangi.

78
00:07:34,787 --> 00:07:36,038
Sudahlah.

79
00:07:37,165 --> 00:07:40,418
Eun-ju, banyak lagi
yang awak perlu belajar.

80
00:07:40,501 --> 00:07:41,335
Belajar apa?

81
00:07:41,919 --> 00:07:46,424
"Jangan bercinta dengan rakan sekerja,
walaupun leher awak diacu pisau."

82
00:07:46,507 --> 00:07:47,633
Orang tak ajarkah?

83
00:07:48,759 --> 00:07:51,637
Saya tak kata
saya nak bercinta dengan dia.

84
00:07:54,932 --> 00:07:56,267
Nanti awak fahamlah.

85
00:07:56,350 --> 00:07:58,394
- Semoga berjaya, Eun-ju.
- Aduhai.

86
00:08:02,607 --> 00:08:06,110
<i>Ini maklum balas tentang cadangan</i>
<i>pasukan awak minggu lepas.</i>

87
00:08:06,652 --> 00:08:08,237
Okey.

88
00:08:09,947 --> 00:08:14,911
<i>Kelemahan, protagonis tiada tarikan.</i>
<i>Penguasaan genre fantasi kurang mantap.</i>

89
00:08:14,994 --> 00:08:17,705
<i>Temanya kabur,</i>
<i>watak-wataknya tiada keserasian.</i>

90
00:08:17,788 --> 00:08:20,666
<i>Ceritanya tak universal</i>
<i>dan tak meyakinkan.</i>

91
00:08:20,750 --> 00:08:22,919
<i>Kekuatan, tiada yang layak disebut.</i>

92
00:08:31,761 --> 00:08:33,596
Hei, Cho!

93
00:08:34,096 --> 00:08:36,974
Hei, saya belum habis cakaplah!

94
00:08:41,354 --> 00:08:42,188
Saya…

95
00:08:42,730 --> 00:08:43,856
Saya nak berhenti.

96
00:08:44,774 --> 00:08:46,943
- Apa?
- Hei! Awak nak berhenti?

97
00:08:47,026 --> 00:08:48,903
- Betul!
- Janganlah begitu.

98
00:08:48,986 --> 00:08:51,030
- Lepaslah.
- Bos memang begitu!

99
00:08:51,113 --> 00:08:52,532
- Gasaklah.
- Fikir dulu.

100
00:08:52,615 --> 00:08:53,616
Tak nak. Tepilah!

101
00:08:53,699 --> 00:08:56,702
Cho! Sabarlah. Cho!

102
00:08:57,286 --> 00:08:58,704
Betulkah dia nak pergi?

103
00:09:04,001 --> 00:09:07,296
Kenapa kamu semua pandang saya?
Saya tak buat salah pun.

104
00:09:08,130 --> 00:09:10,967
Betulkah dia dah berhenti?
Apa kita nak buat?

105
00:09:11,050 --> 00:09:12,468
JI-YEON

106
00:09:12,552 --> 00:09:15,388
<i>Kita perlu jumpa hari ini. Saya serius.</i>

107
00:09:15,471 --> 00:09:16,722
Dia kenapa?

108
00:09:20,393 --> 00:09:21,477
Hei.

109
00:09:21,978 --> 00:09:22,979
Seo Mi-rae!

110
00:09:23,813 --> 00:09:25,481
Lama betul nak sampai sini.

111
00:09:29,235 --> 00:09:31,779
Awak nak ajak saya
belek-belek baju sajakah?

112
00:09:31,862 --> 00:09:34,740
Mestilah tak,
saya pun tahu awak macam mana.

113
00:09:34,824 --> 00:09:38,494
Saya nak ajak bincang
isu penting yang sangat serius.

114
00:09:38,995 --> 00:09:41,247
Isu? Isu apa?

115
00:09:42,623 --> 00:09:45,293
Majlis kahwin An Da-yeong.
Awak nak pakai apa?

116
00:09:46,085 --> 00:09:46,919
Apa?

117
00:09:48,254 --> 00:09:52,091
Awak pergi, bukan?
Takkan awak nak hulur duit saja?

118
00:09:52,883 --> 00:09:55,261
Saya sibuk dengan kerja dan…

119
00:09:55,344 --> 00:09:57,513
Hei! Sebab itulah awak wajib pergi.

120
00:09:57,597 --> 00:10:01,434
Awak patut melaram
dan tunjukkan yang hidup awak berjaya!

121
00:10:01,517 --> 00:10:02,852
Saya berjayakah?

122
00:10:03,352 --> 00:10:05,313
Yang penting, nampak berjaya.

123
00:10:05,396 --> 00:10:07,189
Semua geng sekelas kita pergi.

124
00:10:07,273 --> 00:10:11,068
Takkan awak nak biar saja
You-mi dan Se-june tunjuk romantik?

125
00:10:11,152 --> 00:10:14,530
Memanglah mereka bahagia,
tapi awak tak boleh kalah.

126
00:10:14,614 --> 00:10:17,366
"Aku hidup senang.
Aku di puncak kejayaan."

127
00:10:17,450 --> 00:10:22,246
Kami dah lama berpisah.
Lagipun, apa yang saya nak banggakan?

128
00:10:22,330 --> 00:10:24,373
Baju ini boleh tahan juga.

129
00:10:24,457 --> 00:10:26,000
Pergi cuba pakai.

130
00:10:26,667 --> 00:10:27,710
Cepatlah!

131
00:10:35,718 --> 00:10:38,721
Bukan Se-june kahwin pun.
Drama betullah Ji-Yeon.

132
00:10:43,434 --> 00:10:46,270
Kalau awak pulangkan baju itu, siap awak.

133
00:10:46,354 --> 00:10:49,440
Alah, bukannya awak yang belikan pun.

134
00:10:49,523 --> 00:10:52,777
Saya cikgu seni.
Awak ingat saya banyak duitkah?

135
00:10:52,860 --> 00:10:55,279
Kalau mampu, memang saya belanja.

136
00:10:57,698 --> 00:10:59,700
Kasihan awak, Mi-rae.

137
00:11:00,451 --> 00:11:02,578
Eh, kenapa nak kasihan pula?

138
00:11:03,079 --> 00:11:05,831
Saya sihat. Saya gembira.

139
00:11:05,915 --> 00:11:07,083
Awak tak sunyi?

140
00:11:07,667 --> 00:11:08,793
Sikit pun tak.

141
00:11:11,170 --> 00:11:14,507
Takkanlah awak tak fikir
tentang lelaki langsung?

142
00:11:14,590 --> 00:11:19,053
Awak ingat syarikat saya naikkan gaji saya
kalau saya ada teman lelaki?

143
00:11:19,136 --> 00:11:22,807
Bukankah itu maknanya
bercinta cuma buat saya lebih penat

144
00:11:22,890 --> 00:11:24,892
dan lebih miskin?

145
00:11:24,975 --> 00:11:27,186
Bukan setakat penat badan.

146
00:11:27,269 --> 00:11:31,816
Awak tahu betapa penatnya otak
kalau bercinta dengan lelaki tak matang.

147
00:11:31,899 --> 00:11:35,027
Apa susahnya? Carilah lelaki matang!

148
00:11:35,111 --> 00:11:37,446
Atau lelaki macam awak.

149
00:11:38,030 --> 00:11:40,324
Lelaki macam saya?

150
00:11:40,408 --> 00:11:41,409
Yalah!

151
00:11:41,492 --> 00:11:44,078
- Yang sama perangai.
- Maksudnya?

152
00:11:44,161 --> 00:11:45,871
Awak tak kacau orang,

153
00:11:45,955 --> 00:11:48,249
tapi perangai awak boleh tahan…

154
00:11:49,208 --> 00:11:50,710
dingin.

155
00:11:51,293 --> 00:11:52,753
Carilah lelaki begitu.

156
00:11:53,254 --> 00:11:54,088
Senang.

157
00:11:55,297 --> 00:11:56,716
<i>Saya nak berhenti.</i>

158
00:11:56,799 --> 00:11:59,593
Janganlah, Cho! Bos memang begitu!

159
00:11:59,677 --> 00:12:00,511
Gasaklah.

160
00:12:00,594 --> 00:12:03,639
- Macam mana kami nak kerja tanpa awak?
- Tanyalah bos!

161
00:12:03,723 --> 00:12:07,309
Hei, awak dah gila?
Kenapa nak cari lelaki begitu?

162
00:12:07,393 --> 00:12:10,980
Itu namanya kera sumbang, bukan manusia!

163
00:12:12,231 --> 00:12:14,358
Macam itulah saya rasa tentang awak!

164
00:12:20,614 --> 00:12:22,283
Hei, saya dah balik.

165
00:12:24,660 --> 00:12:26,162
Saya dah baliklah!

166
00:12:26,662 --> 00:12:28,539
<i>Mod rumah diaktifkan.</i>

167
00:12:47,767 --> 00:12:50,853
Aduh, aku dah gila agaknya.
Ini bukannya murah…

168
00:13:09,330 --> 00:13:10,331
Awak serius?

169
00:13:10,414 --> 00:13:11,248
Alamak.

170
00:13:11,749 --> 00:13:15,002
Sayangnya, Cho sikit lagi
nak jadi ketua pasukan.

171
00:13:15,836 --> 00:13:17,087
Sebab Yun Song, ya?

172
00:13:17,963 --> 00:13:19,799
Aduh, siapa nak ganti dia?

173
00:13:20,424 --> 00:13:23,385
Calonnya dah ada?
Atau Pasukan 1 yang ambil alih?

174
00:13:24,470 --> 00:13:25,471
Dengar kata,

175
00:13:25,971 --> 00:13:28,808
kalau bukan Park Kyeong-nam,
mesti Seo Mi-rae.

176
00:13:29,683 --> 00:13:32,186
Apa? Kalau Park Kyeong-nam, saya fahamlah.

177
00:13:32,269 --> 00:13:34,814
Tapi Mi-rae bukan penerbit genre Yun pun.

178
00:13:34,897 --> 00:13:37,441
Penerbit genre cinta
mati-mati tak nak buat.

179
00:13:38,108 --> 00:13:40,486
Sekarang ini jadual Mi-rae lebih kosong.

180
00:13:41,570 --> 00:13:42,780
Selamat pagi.

181
00:13:46,325 --> 00:13:48,410
Apa? Kenapa?

182
00:13:59,505 --> 00:14:00,506
Apa?

183
00:14:00,589 --> 00:14:01,757
Saya? Saya?

184
00:14:06,053 --> 00:14:08,138
Selamat pagi, semua!

185
00:14:08,222 --> 00:14:09,265
Selamat pagi!

186
00:14:09,765 --> 00:14:10,683
Selamat pagi.

187
00:14:14,144 --> 00:14:16,981
Tapi projek Park
akhir-akhir ini lebih berjaya.

188
00:14:17,064 --> 00:14:19,400
Harap-harap bos tugaskan dia.

189
00:14:21,443 --> 00:14:24,697
Mana boleh teka-teka.
Kita tak tahu apa bos fikir.

190
00:14:29,785 --> 00:14:30,953
Jangan risaulah.

191
00:14:33,622 --> 00:14:35,124
Alamak.

192
00:14:38,168 --> 00:14:39,545
<i>Cik Yun!</i>

193
00:14:41,463 --> 00:14:42,506
<i>Cik Yun!</i>

194
00:14:42,590 --> 00:14:44,758
Bukalah pintu, Cik Yun!

195
00:14:46,760 --> 00:14:50,097
Cik Yun! Berilah fail yang dah siap!

196
00:14:50,180 --> 00:14:52,182
Cik Yun!

197
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:01,108
<i>Cik Yun!</i>

198
00:15:02,026 --> 00:15:02,902
YUN SONG

199
00:15:07,406 --> 00:15:09,158
JEJAKA BERHARGA
EPISOD 21

200
00:15:11,702 --> 00:15:12,953
MUAT NAIK SELESAI

201
00:15:16,415 --> 00:15:20,002
<i>Ibarat virus yang berjaya</i>
<i>menembusi benteng sel darah putih,</i>

202
00:15:20,502 --> 00:15:24,798
<i>suatu masa dulu, Yun Song</i>
<i>menguasai kehidupan harian aku.</i>

203
00:15:30,512 --> 00:15:31,889
YUN SONG

204
00:15:36,101 --> 00:15:37,269
Ya, Cik Yun.

205
00:15:37,353 --> 00:15:38,520
<i>Seo?</i>

206
00:15:41,273 --> 00:15:43,567
Awak menangiskah?

207
00:15:44,109 --> 00:15:45,527
<i>Awak dah baca komen?</i>

208
00:15:46,195 --> 00:15:48,864
<i>Orang mengata saya macam-macam!</i>

209
00:15:50,574 --> 00:15:52,993
Sekarang dah pukul 3 pagi.

210
00:15:53,077 --> 00:15:56,580
<i>Orang takkan berhenti hentam saya</i>
<i>sampai saya mati, ya?</i>

211
00:15:56,664 --> 00:16:00,209
<i>Tapi kenapa saya pula?</i>
<i>Kenapa saya yang kena mampus?</i>

212
00:16:00,292 --> 00:16:02,378
<i>Kamu semua yang celaka!</i>

213
00:16:04,964 --> 00:16:05,965
<i>Tidak!</i>

214
00:16:06,507 --> 00:16:08,008
Jangan harap.

215
00:16:25,484 --> 00:16:27,820
PEJABAT EKSEKUTIF
ADA

216
00:16:27,903 --> 00:16:29,738
Bos, ini Seo Mi-rae.

217
00:16:29,822 --> 00:16:31,198
Masuklah.

218
00:16:34,284 --> 00:16:37,287
Saya lalu di Raturer Macaron
selepas makan tadi.

219
00:16:37,371 --> 00:16:38,998
Saya tahu bos suka…

220
00:16:44,753 --> 00:16:47,798
Saya tak tahu awak pun ada di sini.

221
00:16:47,881 --> 00:16:51,010
Ya, kebetulan saya pun lalu di kedai itu.

222
00:16:52,094 --> 00:16:54,013
Duduklah. Mari bincang bertiga.

223
00:16:57,891 --> 00:17:00,477
Alamak, manisnya. Manis sangat!

224
00:17:00,561 --> 00:17:02,604
- Minum kopi sikit.
- Okey.

225
00:17:06,984 --> 00:17:08,819
Ini kopi… Kopi…

226
00:17:09,570 --> 00:17:13,157
- Yirgacheffe.
- Kopi Cheffe! Ya, Cheffe.

227
00:17:14,658 --> 00:17:19,121
Selama ini saya ingatkan
kamu berdua tak ramah sangat.

228
00:17:20,122 --> 00:17:21,498
Saya nak tanya tentang…

229
00:17:21,582 --> 00:17:22,666
Okey!

230
00:17:23,834 --> 00:17:26,879
Peluang macam ini
datang sekali saja, tahu?

231
00:17:26,962 --> 00:17:28,630
Jelaskan sebab

232
00:17:29,131 --> 00:17:34,344
kamu layak uruskan Yun Song,
penulis nombor satu Naemo.

233
00:17:34,428 --> 00:17:35,929
Okey, mula-mula saya nak…

234
00:17:36,013 --> 00:17:40,350
Walaupun kamu berdua malas ikut
setiap kali saya ajak makan-makan,

235
00:17:40,934 --> 00:17:42,770
saya tak simpan dendam.

236
00:17:42,853 --> 00:17:46,106
Saya akan buat pilihan
berdasarkan kebolehan kamu.

237
00:17:46,607 --> 00:17:49,526
Jadi, relaks dan silalah cakap.

238
00:17:50,110 --> 00:17:51,403
Orang paling layak

239
00:17:51,487 --> 00:17:55,115
uruskan penulis nombor satu kita,
mestilah tak lain tak bukan…

240
00:17:55,199 --> 00:17:56,158
Saya tarik diri.

241
00:17:57,785 --> 00:17:59,995
Walaupun saya masuk Naemo awal sikit,

242
00:18:00,079 --> 00:18:04,541
Seo Mi-rae terbukti cekap
uruskan penulis dan rancang projek.

243
00:18:04,625 --> 00:18:09,046
Saya dah fikir masak-masak
dan rasa awak patut rebut peluang ini.

244
00:18:09,129 --> 00:18:10,172
Okey.

245
00:18:10,255 --> 00:18:13,592
Tapi saya tak berani ambil tempat
orang yang secekap dia

246
00:18:13,675 --> 00:18:16,303
dan uruskan Cik Yun buat kali kedua.

247
00:18:16,386 --> 00:18:17,596
Jangan rendah diri.

248
00:18:18,180 --> 00:18:21,391
Penulis yang Park uruskan
sentiasa keluarkan komik hit.

249
00:18:21,475 --> 00:18:23,310
Eloklah dia jaga Cik Yun.

250
00:18:23,393 --> 00:18:26,188
Lagipun, dia sendiri kata yang projek saya

251
00:18:27,064 --> 00:18:29,483
tiada kekuatan yang layak disebut.

252
00:18:31,026 --> 00:18:34,947
Meja Cik Yun dah lengkap terhidang,
jadi tak perlulah nak risau.

253
00:18:35,030 --> 00:18:38,075
Okey, awak telanlah
apa-apa yang dia hidangkan.

254
00:18:38,158 --> 00:18:39,159
Cukuplah.

255
00:18:40,369 --> 00:18:44,915
Kamu berdua tak nak uruskan dia.
Senang kata begitulah, bukan?

256
00:18:47,334 --> 00:18:48,794
Okey, saya faham.

257
00:18:51,255 --> 00:18:56,051
Tapi kalau kamu tak ada minat,
kenapa kamu masuk industri komik web?

258
00:18:57,136 --> 00:18:59,388
Ini tidak, sibuk tengok jam nak balik.

259
00:19:00,139 --> 00:19:02,224
Lupakan sajalah. Kamu boleh keluar.

260
00:19:04,101 --> 00:19:05,185
Seo, awak buatlah.

261
00:19:06,353 --> 00:19:07,187
Apa?

262
00:19:07,271 --> 00:19:09,731
Awak cuma jaga enam penulis saja.

263
00:19:09,815 --> 00:19:10,858
Tapi…

264
00:19:10,941 --> 00:19:15,320
Lagipun, awak yang cadangkan
dia tulis genre cinta mula-mula dulu.

265
00:19:15,404 --> 00:19:18,782
Ya, tapi saya serahkan projeknya
kepada penerbit lain.

266
00:19:18,866 --> 00:19:20,117
Itu bukan genre saya.

267
00:19:20,200 --> 00:19:21,577
Saya tak tahu pula.

268
00:19:22,286 --> 00:19:25,289
Kalau hal ini dah selesai,
saya nak minta diri.

269
00:19:25,372 --> 00:19:27,666
- Saya ada mesyuarat.
- Pergilah.

270
00:19:27,749 --> 00:19:28,584
Okey.

271
00:19:29,251 --> 00:19:30,210
Saya pergi dulu.

272
00:19:34,590 --> 00:19:35,591
Tumpang lalu.

273
00:19:40,929 --> 00:19:43,015
Tiba-tiba ada mesyuarat?

274
00:19:44,516 --> 00:19:45,851
Pergilah.

275
00:19:54,484 --> 00:19:55,652
Mesyuarat konon.

276
00:19:58,947 --> 00:19:59,865
Macam mana?

277
00:20:04,411 --> 00:20:05,329
Bos pilih awak?

278
00:20:08,707 --> 00:20:11,877
Park Kyeong-nam bawa makaron sekotak.

279
00:20:12,377 --> 00:20:14,421
- Siapa yang beritahu dia?
- Apa?

280
00:20:15,088 --> 00:20:16,965
Hei, bukan sayalah.

281
00:20:17,549 --> 00:20:19,218
Jadi…

282
00:20:19,718 --> 00:20:22,804
Berapa lama awak kena uruskan Yun Song?

283
00:20:24,056 --> 00:20:25,974
- Entah.
- Berapa lama?

284
00:20:26,058 --> 00:20:28,602
Sampai dia pengsan kepenatan.

285
00:20:29,228 --> 00:20:31,146
Awak boleh buat, Mi-rae.

286
00:20:31,230 --> 00:20:34,233
Kuatkan semangat.
Awak cuma perlu kawal dia.

287
00:20:34,316 --> 00:20:36,235
Kawal Yun Song? Bolehkah?

288
00:20:36,902 --> 00:20:40,906
<i>Sejarah silam muncul semula</i>
<i>untuk menghantui masa depan.</i>

289
00:20:41,406 --> 00:20:42,616
<i>Betul tak saya kata?</i>

290
00:20:42,699 --> 00:20:45,244
<i>Kawan kakak saya kerja di firma guaman.</i>

291
00:20:45,327 --> 00:20:47,537
<i>- Saya nak ke sana esok.</i>
- Baru balik?

292
00:20:47,621 --> 00:20:49,414
<i>- Di Internet, mereka beranilah.</i>
- Apa?

293
00:20:49,498 --> 00:20:52,709
<i>- Saya nak gaduh depan-depan.</i>
- Diam. Yun telefon.

294
00:20:52,793 --> 00:20:54,628
<i>Nak selesai cara baik? Lupakan.</i>

295
00:20:54,711 --> 00:20:56,421
- Bila dia tidur?
<i>- Saya berduit.</i>

296
00:20:56,505 --> 00:20:58,882
<i>- Saya nak telefon kakak.</i>
- Pelik betul.

297
00:21:02,469 --> 00:21:03,387
Dia dah letak!

298
00:21:04,721 --> 00:21:06,473
Saya rasa nak gila.

299
00:21:06,556 --> 00:21:08,100
Bolehkah awak keluar?

300
00:21:09,184 --> 00:21:11,270
Mestilah, ini hari jadi awak.

301
00:21:11,353 --> 00:21:14,022
<i>Iklan yang kita bincang itu</i>
<i>jadi atau tidak?</i>

302
00:21:14,106 --> 00:21:15,857
Janganlah risau sangat.

303
00:21:15,941 --> 00:21:18,277
<i>Mestilah risau. Ini soal duit.</i>

304
00:21:18,360 --> 00:21:20,112
Nanti saya uruskan.

305
00:21:20,195 --> 00:21:23,740
<i>Saya sibuk menulis</i>
<i>sampai nak makan pun tak sempat.</i>

306
00:21:23,824 --> 00:21:25,242
<i>Susah betul, tahu tak?</i>

307
00:21:25,325 --> 00:21:26,994
Saya tahu. Mesti susah.

308
00:21:27,077 --> 00:21:29,162
<i>- Boleh saya rehat bulan ini?</i>
- Apa?

309
00:21:29,246 --> 00:21:31,581
Tapi awak dah berehat bulan lepas.

310
00:21:31,665 --> 00:21:35,794
<i>Kenapalah semua benda kecil pun</i>
<i>orang nak komen?</i>

311
00:21:35,877 --> 00:21:37,713
<i>Sakit jiwa betullah!</i>

312
00:21:38,213 --> 00:21:39,798
Jangan layan komen mereka.

313
00:21:47,097 --> 00:21:48,348
SE-JUNE

314
00:21:53,270 --> 00:21:57,316
<i>Nombor ini tidak dapat dihubungi.</i>
<i>Sila tinggalkan pesanan.</i>

315
00:22:06,575 --> 00:22:07,743
SE-JUNE
12 PANGGILAN

316
00:22:07,826 --> 00:22:08,660
Alamak!

317
00:22:14,291 --> 00:22:15,459
Alamak.

318
00:22:17,586 --> 00:22:18,587
Jawablah!

319
00:22:28,221 --> 00:22:32,726
<i>Itulah pengakhiran kisah cinta aku</i>
<i>yang takkan kembali lagi.</i>

320
00:22:36,396 --> 00:22:40,067
Jangankan nak balik ikut masa,
kejar tren akhir pun tak sempat.

321
00:22:40,150 --> 00:22:45,489
Bukankah Yun Song buat awak stres
sampai botak di sebelah sini?

322
00:22:45,572 --> 00:22:47,074
Dah tumbuh balik tak?

323
00:22:47,157 --> 00:22:49,409
- Yakah?
- Saya rasa di sini.

324
00:22:50,369 --> 00:22:51,328
Sebelah sinikah?

325
00:22:51,411 --> 00:22:53,288
Nanti mesti gugur lagi.

326
00:22:53,789 --> 00:22:56,041
Hei, sudahlah.

327
00:22:57,084 --> 00:22:59,044
Awak nak cakap apa tadi, Hye-bin?

328
00:22:59,544 --> 00:23:00,629
Ya, lupa pula…

329
00:23:02,714 --> 00:23:05,425
Awak hadiri mesyuarat itu tak?

330
00:23:16,603 --> 00:23:18,105
Sakitlah!

331
00:23:18,647 --> 00:23:21,191
Alamak, maaflah! Saya tak sengaja.

332
00:23:21,274 --> 00:23:22,609
Awak okey tak?

333
00:23:29,825 --> 00:23:32,327
- Lawanya dia!
- Yalah, awak makin lawa.

334
00:23:32,828 --> 00:23:33,745
Berseri-seri.

335
00:23:33,829 --> 00:23:35,414
Awak makin kuruskah?

336
00:23:36,498 --> 00:23:40,043
Biar betul? Saya dah kata,
jangan pulangkan baju itu.

337
00:23:40,127 --> 00:23:42,629
- Saya tak pulangkan.
- Kenapa tak pakai?

338
00:23:43,463 --> 00:23:47,259
Saya tak rasa nak pakai.
Tak guna nampak cantik hari ini.

339
00:23:47,342 --> 00:23:49,678
- Tapi…
- Seo Mi-rae!

340
00:23:49,761 --> 00:23:51,513
Awak jawab panggilan Ji-yeon saja!

341
00:23:51,596 --> 00:23:53,723
Tak sangka awak datang.
Dengarnya awak sibuk.

342
00:23:53,807 --> 00:23:56,351
- Seronok dapat berkumpul.
- Apa khabar?

343
00:23:56,435 --> 00:23:58,270
Macam-macam saya nak cerita.

344
00:23:58,353 --> 00:24:00,063
Jom borak sambil minum nanti.

345
00:24:00,564 --> 00:24:01,398
Marilah.

346
00:24:01,481 --> 00:24:02,691
<i>Pengantin lelaki!</i>

347
00:24:12,200 --> 00:24:16,872
<i>Stereotaip terserempak kekasih lama</i>
<i>di majlis perkahwinan kawan</i>

348
00:24:18,331 --> 00:24:20,333
<i>tak berlaku kali ini.</i>

349
00:24:20,417 --> 00:24:24,087
Ketibaan bintang hari ini,
dipersilakan pengantin wanita.

350
00:24:27,549 --> 00:24:28,967
Da-yeong!

351
00:24:29,676 --> 00:24:31,511
- Tahniah!
- Cantiknya.

352
00:24:39,394 --> 00:24:41,354
Tahniah!

353
00:24:41,438 --> 00:24:43,106
Tahniah. Semoga berbahagia!

354
00:24:43,190 --> 00:24:44,816
Macam pinang dibelah dua!

355
00:24:46,359 --> 00:24:47,569
Lawa macam bidadari!

356
00:24:54,117 --> 00:24:55,494
Dia cantik, bukan?

357
00:24:55,577 --> 00:24:57,037
- Ya.
- Cantik sangat.

358
00:24:57,120 --> 00:24:59,873
Kami nak pergi minum. Awak ikut, bukan?

359
00:24:59,956 --> 00:25:02,459
Mestilah, saya bawa Mi-rae sekali.

360
00:25:02,542 --> 00:25:03,627
- Bagus.
- Sekejap.

361
00:25:03,710 --> 00:25:05,253
Jangan tak ikut pula.

362
00:25:05,337 --> 00:25:08,131
- Yalah.
- Awak selalu mengelak.

363
00:25:09,508 --> 00:25:10,759
You-mi!

364
00:25:11,259 --> 00:25:12,427
You-mi! Tahniah!

365
00:25:12,511 --> 00:25:14,513
- You-mi datangkah?
- Mana?

366
00:25:16,014 --> 00:25:17,265
Hei!

367
00:25:19,100 --> 00:25:21,269
- Dia dah nak kahwin.
- Betulkah?

368
00:25:21,353 --> 00:25:22,562
- Betul.
- Wah!

369
00:25:22,646 --> 00:25:25,941
- Se-june masih di Amerika?
- Ya, dia balik minggu depan.

370
00:25:26,024 --> 00:25:28,026
Hei, kalau awak kahwin nanti…

371
00:25:30,070 --> 00:25:35,992
<i>Teman wanita yang dicemburui semua,</i>
<i>dengan cincin berlian pada jarinya.</i>

372
00:25:42,666 --> 00:25:48,380
<i>Se-june berjaya menunjuk-nunjuk</i>
<i>tanpa tunjuk muka sekali pun.</i>

373
00:25:49,172 --> 00:25:50,799
- Syabas!
- Saya tumpang gembira.

374
00:25:50,882 --> 00:25:53,051
Patutlah lawa, seri orang bertunang.

375
00:25:53,134 --> 00:25:55,053
Merepeklah! Kamu semua pun lawa.

376
00:26:08,233 --> 00:26:12,028
Saya teringin nak dukung anak begitu
selepas saya kahwin.

377
00:26:12,988 --> 00:26:14,030
Awak nak kahwin?

378
00:26:14,906 --> 00:26:17,576
- Suatu hari nanti.
- Dengan siapa?

379
00:26:20,704 --> 00:26:22,956
Apa-apalah. Mesti awak jumpa jodoh.

380
00:26:23,582 --> 00:26:25,625
Awak okey tak?

381
00:26:26,293 --> 00:26:27,294
Kenapa tanya?

382
00:26:27,794 --> 00:26:29,170
Kenapa cakap begitu?

383
00:26:29,254 --> 00:26:32,924
Kalau cakap tentang masa depan,
awak selalu sebut "saya".

384
00:26:33,883 --> 00:26:36,303
Pernahkah awak sebut "kita"?

385
00:27:00,452 --> 00:27:03,830
<i>Dah lama kita tak jumpa.</i>
<i>Tak sabar nak jumpa esok.</i>

386
00:27:03,913 --> 00:27:06,416
Biar betul?

387
00:27:06,499 --> 00:27:08,126
<i>Aku dah terlupa.</i>

388
00:27:08,793 --> 00:27:12,380
Kenapa semua orang nak menyerabutkan aku?

389
00:27:14,174 --> 00:27:15,383
JEJAKA BERHARGA

390
00:27:16,551 --> 00:27:17,886
EPISOD 107

391
00:27:17,969 --> 00:27:20,013
BERANI AWAK…
SERANG KELUARGA SAYA?

392
00:27:20,513 --> 00:27:21,348
GENGGAM

393
00:27:21,848 --> 00:27:23,767
MAK CIK BUAT APA?
SAYA KECEWA

394
00:27:24,267 --> 00:27:28,063
Ceritanya dah semakin melalut-lalut.

395
00:27:30,315 --> 00:27:32,859
<i>Komik web Naemo paling popular</i>
<i>tiga tahun berturut-turut,</i>

396
00:27:32,942 --> 00:27:35,403
Jejaka Berharga <i>oleh Yun Song</i>.

397
00:27:35,487 --> 00:27:39,407
<i>Kisah cinta Choi Si-woo,</i>
<i>pewaris generasi ketiga Kumpulan SY.</i>

398
00:27:39,491 --> 00:27:42,452
<i>Seperti biasa, heronya kacak tapi biadab.</i>

399
00:27:42,535 --> 00:27:46,665
<i>Tapi klise basi, sisi lembutnya</i>
<i>cuma muncul apabila dia bersama heroin.</i>

400
00:27:46,748 --> 00:27:50,877
<i>Kisahnya bercampur elemen aksi lasak</i>
<i>dan muslihat keluarga kaya-raya.</i>

401
00:27:51,378 --> 00:27:53,588
<i>Plot cinta utamanya dicedok sana sini</i>

402
00:27:53,672 --> 00:27:57,676
<i>sampaikan Hans Christian Andersen pun</i>
<i>nak bangkit dari kubur dan saman dia.</i>

403
00:27:58,176 --> 00:28:00,595
<i>Semasa projek pembinaan resort di Cebu,</i>

404
00:28:00,679 --> 00:28:03,765
<i>Choi Si-woo pergi meluncur,</i>
<i>dihanyutkan ombak,</i>

405
00:28:03,848 --> 00:28:07,519
<i>tapi diselamatkan Eun Na-ra,</i>
<i>protagonis wanita yang bercuti,</i>

406
00:28:07,602 --> 00:28:09,938
<i>lalu jatuh cinta dengan gadis itu.</i>

407
00:28:12,774 --> 00:28:13,692
JEJAKA BERHARGA

408
00:28:13,775 --> 00:28:15,026
<i>YS dah kering idea.</i>

409
00:28:15,110 --> 00:28:17,696
<i>Membazir duit.</i>
<i>Baik belanja mak ayah makan.</i>

410
00:28:17,779 --> 00:28:19,030
<i>Nombor satu? Siapa baca?</i>

411
00:28:19,114 --> 00:28:20,740
<i>Naemo akan jatuh. Buanglah YS.</i>

412
00:28:20,824 --> 00:28:22,492
<i>Uruskan penulis baik-baik.</i>

413
00:28:22,575 --> 00:28:24,953
<i>Ini ubat hipotensi terbaik.</i>
<i>Naik darah dibuatnya.</i>

414
00:28:25,036 --> 00:28:27,706
<i>Berhenti main Insta, YS. Kasihan peminat.</i>

415
00:28:28,206 --> 00:28:29,374
YUN SONG

416
00:28:30,125 --> 00:28:32,210
<i>Yun Song gaduh dengan pembaca lagi.</i>

417
00:28:32,293 --> 00:28:34,796
<i>YS dikecam selepas tuju mesej individu.</i>

418
00:28:34,879 --> 00:28:37,882
<i>Peminat bengang penulis popular</i>
<i>tiba-tiba berehat.</i>

419
00:28:54,315 --> 00:28:55,442
Datang cari snek?

420
00:28:56,818 --> 00:28:57,652
Tak, saya…

421
00:29:09,456 --> 00:29:10,874
<i>Menyakitkan hati.</i>

422
00:29:12,125 --> 00:29:13,126
<i>Pentingkan diri.</i>

423
00:29:14,127 --> 00:29:15,920
<i>Tak fikir orang lain langsung.</i>

424
00:29:16,004 --> 00:29:18,131
- Seo.
- Ya?

425
00:29:20,216 --> 00:29:21,551
Lama lagi awak duduk?

426
00:29:24,637 --> 00:29:26,556
Lima minit lagi.

427
00:29:28,641 --> 00:29:29,476
Okey.

428
00:30:08,097 --> 00:30:09,682
Indahnya cuaca hari ini.

429
00:30:17,857 --> 00:30:20,777
Seo, tentang serahan hasil kerja Yun Song…

430
00:30:20,860 --> 00:30:22,779
Saya ambil daripada siapa, ya?

431
00:30:22,862 --> 00:30:24,197
Park Kyeong-nam.

432
00:30:25,240 --> 00:30:26,241
Apa?

433
00:30:27,659 --> 00:30:29,494
Park?

434
00:30:37,085 --> 00:30:40,296
Macam mana ada di sini?
Awak tak perasan sebab kecil sangatkah?

435
00:30:43,049 --> 00:30:45,301
Saya datang untuk proses serahan.

436
00:30:45,802 --> 00:30:47,971
Proses serahan?

437
00:30:52,141 --> 00:30:55,103
Lima minit lagi. Bilik mesyuarat.

438
00:30:56,521 --> 00:30:58,481
- Lima minit?
- Ya.

439
00:31:00,525 --> 00:31:01,526
Okey.

440
00:31:08,491 --> 00:31:12,078
Ratingnya paling rendah,
tapi jualannya kekal stabil.

441
00:31:12,161 --> 00:31:14,038
Kontrak iklan masih ada tiga.

442
00:31:14,706 --> 00:31:17,458
Kita boleh alihkan satu
kepada komik web lain.

443
00:31:17,542 --> 00:31:19,252
Kadar kliknya agak tinggi,

444
00:31:19,335 --> 00:31:21,880
jadi kita boleh tarik klien baru.

445
00:31:22,463 --> 00:31:25,633
<i>Mesti kau seronok</i>
<i>dapat lepas tangan, bukan?</i>

446
00:31:25,717 --> 00:31:28,094
Boleh awak tengok fail yang saya hantar?

447
00:31:32,807 --> 00:31:35,310
<i>Tengoklah, kuku dia punyalah rapi.</i>

448
00:31:35,810 --> 00:31:37,645
<i>Kutikelnya langsung tak nampak.</i>

449
00:31:37,729 --> 00:31:38,730
- Seo.
- Ya?

450
00:31:40,857 --> 00:31:41,858
Kliklah fail itu.

451
00:31:44,652 --> 00:31:45,778
Okey.

452
00:31:45,862 --> 00:31:50,158
Ini maklum balas oleh pasukan saya
kepada En. Cho tentang <i>Jejaka Berharga.</i>

453
00:31:50,241 --> 00:31:52,201
- Bacalah kalau perlu.
- Okey.

454
00:31:52,702 --> 00:31:53,786
Satu lagi…

455
00:31:58,166 --> 00:32:02,253
DARIPADA: PARK KYEONG-NAM
KUPON SAUNA/PENGINAPAN

456
00:32:02,337 --> 00:32:03,171
Apa ini?

457
00:32:04,631 --> 00:32:07,091
Cho kata awak mungkin perlukannya.

458
00:32:08,593 --> 00:32:11,930
Tak perlu, sebab apa-apa pun,
saya akan balik tidur di rumah.

459
00:32:13,473 --> 00:32:15,224
Okey. Tak apa.

460
00:32:16,601 --> 00:32:19,354
Apa-apa pun, proses serahan dah siap.

461
00:32:19,938 --> 00:32:21,773
Ada nak tanya apa-apa?

462
00:32:22,649 --> 00:32:23,483
Tak ada.

463
00:32:24,317 --> 00:32:25,526
Okey.

464
00:32:42,543 --> 00:32:43,670
Masa makan.

465
00:32:46,214 --> 00:32:47,215
Cepatnya?

466
00:32:48,508 --> 00:32:50,218
Hari ini awak kena jumpa Yun.

467
00:32:51,177 --> 00:32:53,012
Jom, saya belanja makan <i>unadon</i>.

468
00:32:54,555 --> 00:32:56,849
Baiknya awak.

469
00:33:00,520 --> 00:33:01,854
- Jom.
- Jom makan!

470
00:33:02,355 --> 00:33:05,525
Entah kenapa saya loya kalau makan halia.

471
00:33:05,608 --> 00:33:07,026
Dia tak faham.

472
00:33:07,110 --> 00:33:09,445
Rasa halia yang buat <i>unadon </i>ada umph.

473
00:33:09,529 --> 00:33:10,947
Betul!

474
00:33:11,948 --> 00:33:13,992
Laparnya. Menyesal tak pesan makanan.

475
00:33:40,351 --> 00:33:41,185
Seo Mi-rae!

476
00:33:42,228 --> 00:33:44,647
Cik Yun! Awalnya awak sampai.

477
00:33:44,731 --> 00:33:48,067
Jom makan sebelum mesyuarat.
Sempat, bukan?

478
00:33:48,151 --> 00:33:50,028
Kamu pergilah dulu.

479
00:33:50,111 --> 00:33:51,696
Cepatlah. Saya lapar!

480
00:33:52,739 --> 00:33:53,948
- Pergi dulu.
- Laparnya.

481
00:33:54,032 --> 00:33:55,283
Selamat makan, cik.

482
00:34:20,641 --> 00:34:21,476
Sedapnya.

483
00:34:23,561 --> 00:34:27,148
- Risau nak kerja dengan sayakah?
- Apa? Mana ada.

484
00:34:28,566 --> 00:34:31,402
Kalau Cho tak sakit,
kami boleh teruskan saja.

485
00:34:31,486 --> 00:34:33,654
Tapi itulah, dia lemah sangat.

486
00:34:33,738 --> 00:34:37,658
<i>Kami dah lama tak jumpa,</i>
<i>tapi dia masih tak tahu apa-apa.</i>

487
00:34:37,742 --> 00:34:40,203
Dah tiga tahun. Mari kita berusaha.

488
00:34:40,286 --> 00:34:43,206
Ya, saya tak sabar nak bekerjasama.

489
00:34:43,790 --> 00:34:47,460
Kalau bukan kerana awak,
saya tentu takkan berjaya.

490
00:34:49,796 --> 00:34:52,715
Awak mesti boleh berjaya tanpa saya.

491
00:34:53,925 --> 00:34:55,009
Ya, betul juga.

492
00:35:00,264 --> 00:35:04,268
Heroinnya selalu dianiaya
oleh keluarga mentua yang benci dia

493
00:35:04,352 --> 00:35:07,855
sebelum Choi Si-woo muncul,
tunjuk hebat dan selamatkan dia…

494
00:35:07,939 --> 00:35:10,525
Pembaca dah jemu.

495
00:35:11,234 --> 00:35:13,820
Baru-baru ini, mak cik suaminya terlampau…

496
00:35:13,903 --> 00:35:15,029
Biar benar.

497
00:35:16,197 --> 00:35:20,034
Awak nak hero yang kaya dan kacak
berhenti tunjuk hebat?

498
00:35:21,744 --> 00:35:25,414
Bukan itu masalahnya.
Keluarganya tak habis-habis benci…

499
00:35:25,498 --> 00:35:27,959
Kenapa pembaca mengutuk tapi tetap baca?

500
00:35:28,042 --> 00:35:32,130
Mereka nak saya tulis cerita
yang boleh dijadikan modal mengutuk.

501
00:35:32,755 --> 00:35:37,176
Aduhai, inilah yang saya risau.

502
00:35:37,260 --> 00:35:38,094
Apa?

503
00:35:39,720 --> 00:35:40,555
Risau apa?

504
00:35:41,806 --> 00:35:44,517
Saya tahu awak pandai,

505
00:35:45,017 --> 00:35:48,396
tapi kita berdua tahu
cara kita sebenarnya tak serasi.

506
00:35:52,817 --> 00:35:55,987
Beritahulah pengarah
awak tak nak kerja dengan saya.

507
00:35:56,737 --> 00:36:00,658
Tapi hal itu bukan masalah,
kalau kita boleh berbincang.

508
00:36:02,201 --> 00:36:03,536
Macam dulu-dulu.

509
00:36:09,750 --> 00:36:10,918
Macam dulu-dulu.

510
00:36:11,002 --> 00:36:13,588
Berilah fail yang dah siap!

511
00:36:14,088 --> 00:36:15,506
Macam dulu-dulu.

512
00:36:16,007 --> 00:36:17,341
Macam dulu-dulu.

513
00:36:17,425 --> 00:36:18,843
Cik Yun!

514
00:36:21,512 --> 00:36:25,433
Maaf kalau mengganggu.
Ada tetamu nak jumpa, Cik Yun.

515
00:36:25,516 --> 00:36:27,852
- Betulkah? Okey.
- Okey.

516
00:36:28,352 --> 00:36:29,520
- Masuklah.
- Helo.

517
00:36:29,604 --> 00:36:31,272
- Hai. Apa khabar?
- Helo.

518
00:36:31,355 --> 00:36:32,273
Lama tak jumpa.

519
00:36:32,356 --> 00:36:35,943
Ini Seo Mi-rae,
penerbit yang uruskan Cik Yun.

520
00:36:36,027 --> 00:36:36,944
Okey.

521
00:36:37,028 --> 00:36:38,279
- Helo.
- Helo.

522
00:36:39,488 --> 00:36:40,698
Saya Min Jun-young.

523
00:36:40,781 --> 00:36:43,159
- Seo Mi-rae. Helo.
- Selamat berkenalan.

524
00:36:43,242 --> 00:36:44,785
- Duduklah.
- Terima kasih.

525
00:36:46,621 --> 00:36:50,416
DU baru lancarkan simulasi janji temu baru

526
00:36:50,499 --> 00:36:52,835
yang gunakan watak Choi Si-woo.

527
00:36:52,919 --> 00:36:55,630
Cik Yun dah jumpa dia
untuk bincangkan kontrak.

528
00:36:56,214 --> 00:36:59,550
Simulasi janji temu? Macam permainankah?

529
00:36:59,634 --> 00:37:03,304
Macam aplikasi janji temu,
lebih realistik daripada permainan.

530
00:37:04,513 --> 00:37:05,848
Apa namanya?

531
00:37:05,932 --> 00:37:06,933
Boyfriend on Demand.

532
00:37:11,312 --> 00:37:13,940
Nampak tak? Saya dah cakap dia begini.

533
00:37:14,023 --> 00:37:16,859
Dia memang nak muntah
dengar benda jiwang-jiwang.

534
00:37:17,360 --> 00:37:19,320
- Bukan begitu. Saya…
- Tak apa.

535
00:37:19,403 --> 00:37:21,072
Ramai beri reaksi begitu.

536
00:37:23,324 --> 00:37:24,992
Saya nak jumpa hari ini

537
00:37:25,076 --> 00:37:28,412
sebab pasukan perancang kami
suka watak ciptaan awak

538
00:37:28,496 --> 00:37:32,500
dan cadangkan kami guna hero
daripada komik awak yang lain.

539
00:37:33,459 --> 00:37:36,087
- Hero komik lain?
- Ya.

540
00:37:37,004 --> 00:37:40,675
Itu saya boleh faham
sebab Choi Si-woo memang popular.

541
00:37:40,758 --> 00:37:43,594
Tapi hero lain tak hebat macam dia.

542
00:37:43,678 --> 00:37:45,972
Mereka macam Si-woo cap ayam.

543
00:37:49,767 --> 00:37:52,270
- Memang betul pun!
- Dia kelakar, bukan?

544
00:37:52,353 --> 00:37:53,771
Maksud dia…

545
00:37:53,854 --> 00:37:58,484
Ya, ada ahli pasukan kami kata watak lain
tak menyerlah macam Si-woo,

546
00:37:58,567 --> 00:38:04,073
jadi saya nak dengar pendapat awak
sebelum buat usul rasmi.

547
00:38:04,699 --> 00:38:05,950
Kalau begitu…

548
00:38:06,909 --> 00:38:09,996
Apa kata kita guna pesaing hero?

549
00:38:11,664 --> 00:38:14,000
- Ya, itu…
- Pesaing hero?

550
00:38:14,583 --> 00:38:15,584
Ya, begini…

551
00:38:15,668 --> 00:38:20,339
Watak hero dan pesaing dalam komik Cik Yun
ada daya tarikan yang berbeza,

552
00:38:20,423 --> 00:38:22,842
jadi heroinnya dalam dilema
sampai akhir cerita.

553
00:38:22,925 --> 00:38:23,759
Ya.

554
00:38:23,843 --> 00:38:26,053
Contohnya Hong-ju, <i>Pakwe Hisap Darah</i>.

555
00:38:26,137 --> 00:38:29,473
Dia terlalu popular sampai awak
terpaksa bunuh wataknya.

556
00:38:29,557 --> 00:38:30,683
Betul.

557
00:38:30,766 --> 00:38:33,686
Episod akhir <i>Itukah Kata Ketua?</i>
dapat rating empat

558
00:38:33,769 --> 00:38:36,689
sebab peminat pesaing hero
sabotaj ratingnya.

559
00:38:36,772 --> 00:38:37,690
Betul.

560
00:38:38,566 --> 00:38:42,903
Gunalah watak pesaing
dalam aplikasi awak dengan slogan ini.

561
00:38:43,738 --> 00:38:46,615
"Kini anda boleh jadikan dia watak utama."

562
00:38:46,699 --> 00:38:48,909
Mesti ia jadi bualan orang.

563
00:38:48,993 --> 00:38:50,536
Wah, saya sukalah!

564
00:38:51,746 --> 00:38:53,331
Wah, bunyinya…

565
00:38:56,125 --> 00:38:57,793
"Jadikan dia watak utama!"

566
00:38:58,878 --> 00:38:59,795
Menarik, bukan?

567
00:39:07,094 --> 00:39:08,637
<i>Pintu dibuka.</i>

568
00:39:09,847 --> 00:39:12,433
Kalau saya telefon, tolonglah jawab.

569
00:39:12,516 --> 00:39:13,351
Pergi dulu.

570
00:39:13,434 --> 00:39:15,603
- Tolonglah jawab!
- Okey.

571
00:39:23,319 --> 00:39:24,153
Hai.

572
00:39:24,236 --> 00:39:26,238
Dah berbual dengan tuan pengarah?

573
00:39:26,322 --> 00:39:27,239
Ya.

574
00:39:27,323 --> 00:39:28,240
Cik Seo?

575
00:39:28,741 --> 00:39:31,243
Boleh kita berbual sekejap?

576
00:39:32,828 --> 00:39:33,746
Apa?

577
00:39:33,829 --> 00:39:35,498
<i>Pengulas produk?</i>

578
00:39:35,581 --> 00:39:37,666
Ya. Tak susah sangat pun.

579
00:39:37,750 --> 00:39:39,460
Awak cuma ulas aplikasi kami

580
00:39:39,543 --> 00:39:42,880
selepas cuba sebulan
dengan peralatan yang disediakan.

581
00:39:44,173 --> 00:39:46,926
Tapi apa yang saya patut ulas?

582
00:39:47,718 --> 00:39:50,930
Awak akan ulas pengalaman janji temu.

583
00:39:51,013 --> 00:39:55,101
Komen tentang pasangan awak,
kelebihan dan kekurangan mereka.

584
00:39:56,102 --> 00:39:59,939
Ia cuma simulasi,
bukan janji temu sebenar?

585
00:40:00,022 --> 00:40:02,024
Simulasi yang realistik.

586
00:40:02,650 --> 00:40:05,236
Awak tak suka jiwang-jiwang sangat, bukan?

587
00:40:06,529 --> 00:40:07,363
Betul.

588
00:40:07,446 --> 00:40:10,491
Kami nak tarik pengguna macam awak juga.

589
00:40:10,991 --> 00:40:12,993
Lagipun, saya tahu awak pengguna bijak.

590
00:40:13,577 --> 00:40:18,624
Aplikasi ini masih versi beta,
jadi kami cari maklum balas berkualiti.

591
00:40:19,208 --> 00:40:23,003
Awak akan dibayar,
jadi fikir dulu dan beritahu saya nanti.

592
00:40:24,046 --> 00:40:25,381
Dibayar?

593
00:40:25,464 --> 00:40:28,634
Mestilah, sebab awak perlu
luangkan masa sendiri.

594
00:40:37,810 --> 00:40:39,061
BOYFRIEND ON DEMAND

595
00:40:48,821 --> 00:40:50,614
"Boyfriend on Demand."

596
00:41:15,639 --> 00:41:18,309
"Selaraskan telefon dengan peranti."

597
00:41:25,608 --> 00:41:29,361
<i>Maklumat pengguna</i>
<i>sedang dihantar kepada peranti.</i>

598
00:41:32,406 --> 00:41:35,743
DISAMBUNGKAN

599
00:41:35,826 --> 00:41:38,913
"Pakai cekak pada kepala.
Selesakan diri anda."

600
00:41:38,996 --> 00:41:41,749
"Cekak secara automatik
mengikut saiz kepala"?

601
00:41:41,832 --> 00:41:44,710
"Anda dijemput ke dunia keajaiban."

602
00:41:44,793 --> 00:41:47,046
<i>Proses personalisasi selesai.</i>

603
00:41:47,546 --> 00:41:50,925
<i>Pakai cekak pada kepala.</i>
<i>Selesakan diri anda.</i>

604
00:41:56,430 --> 00:41:58,641
<i>Tekan butang merah pada peranti.</i>

605
00:41:58,724 --> 00:41:59,558
SELESAI

606
00:41:59,642 --> 00:42:03,479
<i>Apabila butang ditekan,</i>
<i>cekak akan menyala dan bersambung.</i>

607
00:42:09,527 --> 00:42:10,361
Apa dah jadi?

608
00:42:39,431 --> 00:42:40,432
Sejuk!

609
00:43:34,028 --> 00:43:34,862
<i>Aku boleh…</i>

610
00:43:36,030 --> 00:43:37,364
<i>Aku boleh bernafas.</i>

611
00:44:31,335 --> 00:44:32,503
Biar betul…

612
00:44:41,303 --> 00:44:42,262
Nanti dulu.

613
00:44:43,931 --> 00:44:45,683
JEJAKA BERHARGA

614
00:44:46,266 --> 00:44:47,267
Ini…

615
00:44:47,351 --> 00:44:49,269
Ini Choi Si-woo!

616
00:44:54,400 --> 00:44:55,609
<i>Tahniah, Seo Mi-rae,</i>

617
00:44:55,693 --> 00:44:58,028
<i>atas pertemuan dengan calon pertama!</i>

618
00:45:05,202 --> 00:45:07,079
Awak okey?

619
00:48:13,015 --> 00:48:14,766
Terjemahan sari kata oleh FZA

